# PLAYER::GET_MAX_WANTED_LEVEL

## Summary
Gets the players max wanted level

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the maximum wanted level the player can get.
Ranges from 0 to 5.
